WESTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
DOMINICAN REPUBLIC TO TURKS AND CAICOS ISLANDS.
DISTRESS SIGNAL RECEIVED FROM 55 FOOT M/V SUMMER ISLE,
WHITE HULL, SEVEN PERSONS ON BOARD,
LUPERON (19-54.0N 070-57.0W) TO
GRAND TURK ISLAND (21-28.3N 071-08.3W).

ASSIST IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO RCC MIAMI,
PHONE: 305 415 6800, E-MAIL: RCCMIAMI@USCG.MIL.
